  <titles>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">Civil Service Annuity Prompt Payment Act</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">A bill to amend chapter 83 of title 5, United States Code, to provide that unless individuals who are entitled to civil service retirement benefits receive their initial annuity payments promptly, such individuals shall be entitled to receive interest on the delayed payments.</title>
